# Maven build output
target/

# Brainstorming/design docs from the superpowers skills. These are planning
# artifacts rather than user-facing docs; they stay local like session notes.
docs/

# Runtime logs. The game currently writes error.log in the process CWD
# (src/error.log under `mvn exec:exec`). See Log.java:33 — that path should
# move under the user folder; until then, keep any *.log out of the repo.
*.log

# Runtime assets from the commercial/prod build — not part of the open-source repo.
src/data/graphics/
src/data/audio/
src/data/fonts/
src/data/fontMetamorphous.fnt

# Development notes — explicitly ignored from commits.
# Only README.md and CHANGELOG.md are meant to be tracked markdown files.
# If you add a new *.md (session notes, analysis, plan, etc.), add its
# filename to this list. See CLAUDE.md for the rationale.
CLAUDE.md
asset_list.md
code-optimizations.md
optimize.md
session-one.md
session-two.md
summary-phase-1.md
todo.md
